    "en": {
      "title": "The formation of the new alliance under the leadership of Vimal",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Independent Party Union says that a new political alliance led by Mr. Wimal Weerawansa will be formed on the 4th of next month.",
        "Mr. Vasudeva Nanayakkara, the leader of the Democratic Left Front, said that the name of the new political alliance will also be announced on that day.",
        "Several rounds of discussions regarding the new alliance to be unveiled at the National Youth Service Council premises were held in recent days with the participation of representatives of the Independent Party Union."
      ],
